 Malt Icebox Cake\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"427\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-427x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-427x640.jpg 427w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-900x1350.jpg 900w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-150x225.jpg 150w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 427px) 100vw, 427px\" data-pin-nopin=\"nopin\" data-pin-url=\"https://joythebaker.com/2025/06/strawberry-malt-icebox-cake/?tp_image_id=57427\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20427%20640\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-427x640.jpg 427w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-900x1350.jpg 900w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-150x225.jpg 150w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308.jpg 1200w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7308-427x640.jpg\"/\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp data-start=\"134\" data-end=\"465\"\u003eStart by lining a 9×5-inch loaf pan with plenty of plastic wrap – like, more than you think. You want enough overhang on all sides so you can wrap the whole thing up snug later. Press a layer of vanilla wafers into the bottom of the pan, rounded side down. This will be the top of your cake once it’s flipped, so think flat and tidy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"467\" data-end=\"911\"\u003eNext, it’s time to make the whipped cream situation sing. In a medium bowl, whisk together the malted milk powder, powdered sugar, and just a pinch of salt. Add a little splash of the cream and whisk it smooth to keep any lumps at bay. Then, slowly whisk in the rest of the cream along with the vanilla extract. Keep whisking – vigorously if you’re up for it, or grab your electric hand mixer for backup and beat until soft but very sturdy peaks form.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"913\" data-end=\"1220\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"913\" data-end=\"925\"\u003ePro Tip:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eThe stiffer your whipped cream, the sturdier and more sliceable your finished cake will be—think picture-perfect loaf slices. If you stop at looser peaks (like what’s pictured here), the result will be more of a soft, pudding-like scoop situation. Equally delicious – just a matter of preference.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"gallery-5\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg data-pin-title=\"Strawberry Malt Icebox Cake\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"427\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-427x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-427x640.jpg 427w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-900x1350.jpg 900w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-150x225.jpg 150w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 427px) 100vw, 427px\" data-pin-nopin=\"nopin\" data-pin-url=\"https://joythebaker.com/2025/06/strawberry-malt-icebox-cake/?tp_image_id=57428\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20427%20640\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-427x640.jpg 427w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-900x1350.jpg 900w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-150x225.jpg 150w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311.jpg 1200w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7311-427x640.jpg\"/\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg data-pin-title=\"Strawberry Malt Icebox Cake\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"427\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-427x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-427x640.jpg 427w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-900x1350.jpg 900w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-150x225.jpg 150w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 427px) 100vw, 427px\" data-pin-nopin=\"nopin\" data-pin-url=\"https://joythebaker.com/2025/06/strawberry-malt-icebox-cake/?tp_image_id=57429\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20427%20640\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-427x640.jpg 427w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-900x1350.jpg 900w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-150x225.jpg 150w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312.jpg 1200w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7312-427x640.jpg\"/\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003carticle dir=\"auto\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-96\" data-scroll-anchor=\"true\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"64865b74-8c3f-4f6f-bc91-556459c9e80a\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\" tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1222\" data-end=\"1558\"\u003eNow comes the fun part: layering. Spread a layer of whipped cream over the wafers, followed by a single layer of sliced strawberries. Keep going—wafers, cream, strawberries, repeat—until you reach the top of the pan. Finish with one last layer of whipped cream and give yourself a gold star. You just built a cake with no oven required.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1222\" data-end=\"1558\"\u003eOnce the layers are set, gently fold the plastic wrap up and over the top of the cake like you’re tucking it in for a long nap. If any whipped cream is peeking out, patch it up with an extra piece of wrap—no dry tops here. Let the cake chill in the fridge for at least 12 hours (overnight is perfect) so the wafers can soften into tender, cake-like layers and all those flavors have time to cozy up together.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1222\" data-end=\"1558\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-pin-url=\"https://joythebaker.com/2025/06/strawberry-malt-icebox-cake/?tp_image_id=57430\" data-pin-title=\"Strawberry Malt Icebox Cake\" data-pin-nopin=\"nopin\" src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-640x427.jpg 640w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-900x600.jpg 900w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-150x100.jpg 150w, https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20800%20534\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-640x427.jpg 640w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-900x600.jpg 900w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-150x100.jpg 150w, https://joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335.jpg 1200w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7335-1024x683.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1222\" data-end=\"1558\"\u003eWhen you’re ready to serve, gently unwrap your masterpiece and invert it onto a serving plate like the showstopper it is. Peel away the plastic wrap (admire your work here), and top with a few extra strawberry slices and a crumble of vanilla wafers for g\u003cspan\u003eood measure. Slice thick, serve cold, and prepare for a round of well-earned compliments.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"gallery-6\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg data-pin-title=\"Strawberry Malt Icebox Cake\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"427\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7336-427x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_webp,s_webp/joythebaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/IMG_7336-427x640.jpg 